el and Pedro's families get off to a rocky start in the Dominican Republic; Jorge and Anfisa rethink their relationship; Loren and Alexei receive disheartening news; Danielle and Mohamed prepare for court; Russ tries to support Pao.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Lies & Goodbyes\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|07|30}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 18\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n| ShortSummary    = Alex & Loren struggle with a big decision. Chantel & Pedro reach their breaking point. Danielle realizes a hard truth. Mohamed prepares for the trial. Jorge & Anfisa adjust to life without each other. Russ & Pao both get lucrative offers.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Models, Moms & Meltdowns\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|08|06}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 19\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 7\n| ShortSummary    = Chantel & Pedro's situation worsens. Anfisa reveals a shocking secret. Jorge hopes a grand gesture will win Anfisa back. Russ and Pao are at odds once again. Mohamed learns what Danielle has been up to. Danielle fears the worst in court.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = I Do's & I Don'ts\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|08|13}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 20\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 8\n| ShortSummary    = Loren gets a huge surprise; Chantel's relationship with Pedro's family continues to deteriorate; Pao makes a decision that jeopardizes her marriage to Russ; Danielle and Mohamed prepare for court.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Where Do We Go From Here?\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|08|20}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 21\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 9\n| ShortSummary    = Chantel and Pedro prepare to walk down the aisle. Russ and Pao are at a crossroads. Danielle and Mohamed finally face-off. Anfisa and Jorge meet up to discuss the future of their relationship.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = The Couple