pines]]; and Marta & Daya from [[Algeria]].\n\nPaul and Karine married in late 2017 in Brazil.  They welcomed a son Pierre Martins Staehle on March 22, 2019, in [[Manaus, Brazil]].  He weighed 6.9 pounds and measured at 19.7 inches.\n\n'''Episodes'''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: HotPink; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=7% | No. in<br />series\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: HotPink; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=7% | No. in<br />season\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: HotPink; color: #FFFFFF;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: HotPink; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=20% | Original air date\n|-\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = And So It Begins\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|08|05}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 15\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| ShortSummary    = Single mom Rachel prepares to travel to England with a baby; grandmother Angela gets ready to meet her Nigerian prince; Ricky starts to doubt his trip to Colombia; Darcey welcomes Jesse to America; Paul embarks on another journey to Brazil.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Face to Face\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|08|12}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 16\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n| ShortSummary    = Patrick is caught between Myriam and his mother.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Blindsided\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|08|19}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 17\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n| ShortSummary    = Ricky's patience wears thin as he waits for Melissa. Jon adjusts to his new role as a dad. Michael welcomes Angela to Nigeria. Karine takes Paul's test. Tarik arrives in Manila and waits for a suspicious Hazel. Darcey prepares Jesse to meet her daughters.\n| LineColor       = FF69B4\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Family Ties\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2018|08|26}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 18\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| ShortSummary   