 Williams.\n| LineColor       = C89CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 44\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| Title           = Baby Be Mine\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|15}}\n| ShortSummary    = Usman surprises Lisa. Darcey faces the truth. Avery & Ash finally meet. Stephanie risks her health to travel to Australia. David makes plans to go to Ukraine. Geoffrey questions Varya's intentions and Ed worries about Rose and her family's motives.\n| LineColor       = C89CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 45\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 5\n| Title           = Our Lips Are Sealed\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|22}}\n| ShortSummary    = Avery meets Ash's skeptical brother. Ed makes a shocking request. Geoffrey's biggest fear about Varya comes true. Lisa reaches a boiling point. Yolanda hopes she isn't making a mistake. David takes a leap of faith, and Stephanie & Erika finally meet!\n| LineColor       = C89CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 46\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 6\n| Title           = Can't Buy Me Love\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|3|29}}\n| ShortSummary    = Darcey and Tom prepare to meet face to face. Geoffrey questions Varya and the entire trip to Moscow. David anxiously awaits Lana. Stephanie and Erika get romantic. Ed faces regret, while Lisa faces Sojaboy's adoring fans at his music video premiere.\n| LineColor       = C89CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 47\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 7\n| Title           = Who's Crying Now\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2020|4|05}}\n| ShortSummary    = Darcey & Tom finally meet face to face. Yolanda investigates Williams. Ed meets Rosemarie's family. Stephanie & Erika get crafty. Varya's mother questions Geoffrey.  Avery & Ash take a romantic getaway, while Lisa & Usman question their future.\n| LineColor       = C89CCF\n}}\n}}\n\n==''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: What Now?''==\n\nIn March 2017, TLC also announced an original digital spin-off series with the title of ''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: What Now?'' for TLCgo.<ref name=\"more90\" /> The show provided updates on Kirlyam & Alan from season 1, Aleksandra & Josh and Melanie & Devar from season 3, and Alla & Matt and Narkyia & Olulowo from season 4. TLC uploaded all seven episodes online on July 30, 2017. The network combined the segments into TV episodes that aired on September 17 and September 24, 2017, following ''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Before the 90 Days''.\n\nThe ''What Now?'' series was brought back in 2018 for another series of updates. The show provided updates on Kirlyam & Alan from season 1, Danielle & Mohamed from season 2 (although Mohamed did not participate), Melanie & Devar from season 3, and Elizabeth & Andrei and Josh & Aika from season 5; ''Before the 90 Days'' couples featured included Cortney & Antonio and Patrick & Myriam. TLC uploaded all three episodes online in July 2018. The network combined the segments into TV episodes that aired on July 15, 22 and 29, following ''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Happily Ever After?''.\n\nOn April 15, 2019, the ''What Now?'' series returned for a third series of updates.<ref>{{cite web|title=Tensions Peak in Season Three of the TLC GO Digital Original Series \"90 Day Fiance: What Now?\"|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/04/15/tensions-peak-in-season-three-of-the-tlc-go-digital-original-series-90-day-fiance-what-now-986005/20190415tlc01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=April 15, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Pillow Talk''==\n\n===Season 1===\nIn April 2019 it was announced that a spin off featuring a number of previous cast members would take part in a reaction show titled ''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Pillow Talk''. The show premiered alongside season four of ''90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Happily Ever After?'', and featured Darcey & her twin sister Stacey, Loren & Alexei, Annie & David, and Tarik and his brother Dean reacting to that week's episode,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.intouchweekly.com/posts/90-day-fiance-pillow-talk-stars-watch-and-react-to-episodes/|title=Fans Are Going Wild for '90 Day Fiance: Pillow Talk' \u2014 Here's the Gist|date=2019-05-01|website=In Touch Weekly|language=en-US|access-date=2019-05-20}}</ref> with the exception of episode five, \"Dirty Dancing\"; and episode thirteen & fourteen, which are the Tell-All episodes.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tlc.com/tv-shows/90-day-fiance-pillow-talk/|title=90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Pillow Talk {{!}} Watch Full Episodes & More!|website=TLC|language=en-us|access-date=2019-05-20}}</ref>\n\n{{Episode table |background=#B30713 |overall=1 |season=1 |title=65 |airdate=25 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| Title           = Pillow Talk: After The Dust Settles\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|04|28}}\n| ShortSummary    = Your 90 Day favorites invite you into their homes as they watch last night's episode of Happily Ever After? Loren & Alexei, David and Annie, Tarik and his brother, Dean, and Darcey and her twin, Stacey, are watching along and no one is holding back.\n| LineColor       = B30713\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 2\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n| Title           = Pillow Talk: In For a Shock\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|05|06}}\n| ShortSummary    = Your 90 Day favorites invite you into their homes as they watch last night's episode of Happily Ever After? Join Loren and Alexei, David and Annie, Tarik and his brother, Dean, and Darcey and her twin, Stacey, as they dive into all the drama.\n| LineColor       = B30713\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 3\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n| Title           = Pillow Talk: Mistrials of Marriage\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|05|12}}\n| ShortSummary    = Your 90 Day favorites watch last night's episode of Happily Ever After? Loren and Alexei, David and Annie, Tarik and his brother Dean, and Darcey and her twin Stacey, dive into all the drama.\n| LineColor       = B30713\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 4\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| Title       