Devar</center> || rowspan=\"3\"|Season 3\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Kyle & Noon</center> \n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Loren & Alexei</center> \n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Chantel & Pedro</center> || rowspan=\"2\" |Season 4\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Jorge & Anfisa</center>\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Molly & Luis</center>|| rowspan=\"4\" |Season 5\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" |<center>David & Annie</center>\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Nicole & Azan</center>\n| colspan=\"2\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Elizabeth & Andrei</center>\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Ashley & Jay</center>|| rowspan=\"2\" |Season 6\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | <center>Colt & Larissa</center>\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: #D3D3D3\" |\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CMain|Main}}\n|}\n\n====Season 1====\nReturning couples included season one's Russ & Paola; season two's Danielle & Mohamed and Brett & Daya; and season three's Melanie & Devar, Loren & Alexei, and Kyle & Noon. The first season concluded in November 2016 with a two-part \"Tell All\" special.\n\n'''Episodes'