ews|title=\u201990 Day Fiance\u2019 Gets Season 5 Renewal, Second Spinoff at TLC (Exclusive)|url=http://www.thewrap.com/90-day-fiance-happily-ever-after-before-the-90-days-tlc/|work=thewrap.com|author=Tony Maglio|date=2016-11-11|accessdate=2017-06-11}}</ref><ref name=\"more90\">{{cite news|title=TLC Announces An Aggressive 2017-2018 Upfront Slate With 120 More Hours Of Original Programming|url=https://corporate.discovery.com/discovery-newsroom/tlc-announces-an-aggressive-2017-2018-upfront-slate-with-120-more-hours-of-original-programming/|work=[[Discovery Channel]]|date=March 28, 2017}}</ref>\n\n====Season 1====\nThe premise follows six couples - Paul and Karine from [[Brazil]], Darcey and Jesse from the [[Netherlands]], Larry and Jenny from the [[Philippines]], Cortney and Antonio from [[Spain]], Sean and Abby from [[Haiti]], and Patrick and Myriam from [[France]] - as they start a relationship before the K-1 Visa process begins. It premiered on August 6, 2017.<ref>{{cite news|title=Get a Sneak Peek of TLC\u2019s New Series '90 Day Fianc\u00e9: Before the 90 Days\u2019, Meet the Cast|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/entertainment/news/tlcs-new-series-90-day-fianc-before-the-90-days-meet-the-cast-w492813|work=[[Us Weekly]]|date=July 18, 2017}}</ref>\n\n'''Episodes'''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"width:100%;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: #B30713; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=7% | No. in<br>series\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: #B30713; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=7% | No. in<br>season\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: #B30713; color: #FFFFFF;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"background-color: #B30713; color: #FFFFFF;\" width=20% | Original air date\n|-\n{{Episode list\n| Title           = Bon Voyage!\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2017|08|06}}\n| EpisodeNumber   = 1\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| ShortSummary    = Three Americans who feel they've met their potential soul mates online prepare to travel internationally to