becca & Zied from [[Tunisia]]; and Timothy & Jeniffer from [[Colombia]].<ref name=\"90 Day Fianc\u00e9 2019 News\"/>\n\n{{Episode table |background=#689CCF |overall=3 |season=3 |title=65 |airdate=25 |episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 26\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 1\n| Title           = Crazy in Love\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|08|04}}\n| ShortSummary    = Caesar plans to see his dream woman after years of talking online. Timothy is stuck in a love triangle. Rebecca keeps a secret from her Tunisian boyfriend. Avery prepares to meet a man who lives in a war zone. Darcey is back for another shot at love!\n| LineColor       = 689CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 27\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 2\n| Title           = Pack Your Bags\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|08|11}}\n| ShortSummary    = Avery hits a major roadblock on her way to Lebanon. Angela asks her daughter for a favor that would be life-changing. Caesar must convince Maria to go to Mexico. Darcey receives an interesting call and has Rebecca been 100% truthful with Zied?\n| LineColor       = 689CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 28\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 3\n| Title           = Little Lies\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|08|18}}\n| ShortSummary    = Angela deals with more issues surrounding Michael. Darcey gets ready to meet her new British man. Ben worries his Kenyan love interest isn't ready to become a stepmom. Avery finally meets her Syrian fianc\u00e9 Omar. Rebecca digs into Zied's past.\n| LineColor       = 689CCF\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber   = 29\n| EpisodeNumber2  = 4\n| Title           = Love is a Battlefield\n| OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2019|08|25}}\n| ShortSummary    = Tim & Jeniffer clash on day 1 in Colombia, Caesar heads to Mexico to meet Maria, Darcey gets emotional in London, Rebecca sees a different side to Zied in Tunisia, and Avery's mom causes friction at dinner when she expresses her skepticism of Omar.\n| LineColor       = 689CCF\n}}